  "title": "Two round white and silver UFOs were spotted in Curitiba-PR [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/two-round-white-and-silver-ufos-were-spotted-in-curitiba-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1a4",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 12th, 1996</strong>. Time: 17h00. Duration: 10 minutes. Two people in the Cotolengo region, Curitiba, State of Paraná, observed two unidentified flying objects in the shape of white and silver balls moving in the eastern sector of the city. According to the witnesses&#8217; report, the objects were flying &#8220;lower than an aerobatic aircraft&#8221; and they were at a speed &#8220;equal to that of an airplane&#8221;, staying close to each other on their East-West trajectory. The sighting was carried out with the naked eye and in a clear sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.441. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Cotolengo, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
